OL,3,CFormer trampoline park owner spared
OL,4,Cjail for food hygiene violations
OL,6,FA routine food hygiene inspection in
OL,7,FMarch 2024 uncovered multiple failings
OL,8,Fat the premises including black mould
OL,9,Finside the microwave, coffee machines,
OL,10,Fslush machines, ice machines and the
OL,11,Fice cream area.
OL,13,FInspectors found poor food handling
OL,14,Fand crosscontamination practices and
OL,15,Fequipment was used interchangeably for
OL,16,Fraw and readytoeat foods. There was
OL,17,Falso no suitable handwashing
OL,18,Ffacilities in some preparation areas.
