OL,3,CFormer trampoline park owner spared
OL,4,Cjail for food hygiene violations
OL,6,FCllr Norma Mackie, Cabinet Member for
OL,7,FShared Regulatory Services at Cardiff
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "Food safety is
OL,9,Fessential to protect the public. This
OL,10,Fcase involved a long list of serious
OL,11,Fhygiene failings over several
OL,12,Finspections. While improvements were
OL,13,Feventually made, businesses must
OL,14,Falways meet legal standards,
OL,15,Fespecially those catering for children
OL,16,Fand families.
OL,18,F"We will continue to take appropriate
OL,19,Faction, including formal enforcement,
OL,20,Fwhenever businesses fail to comply
OL,21,Fwith food hygiene law."
