OL,4,Cjail for food hygiene violations
OL,6,FA followup inspection at Supajump on
OL,7,FApril 26, 2024, found that although
OL,8,Fmany issues had been addressed, Booth
OL,9,Fhad failed to comply with the Hygiene
OL,10,FImprovement Notice within the required
OL,11,Ftimeframe and had not requested an
OL,12,Fextension.
OL,14,FFurther visits in May and June 2024
OL,15,Fconfirmed all outstanding matters had
OL,16,Fbeen resolved. At a rerating
OL,17,Finspection in August 2024, the
OL,18,Fbusiness was awarded a Food Hygiene
OL,19,FRating of 3 ` Generally Satisfactory.
