OL,3,CFormer trampoline park owner spared
OL,4,Cjail for food hygiene violations
OL,6,FBooth was fined #900, ordered to pay
OL,7,F#500 in costs, and must pay #40 per
OL,8,Fmonth until the amount is settled in
OL,9,Ffull.
OL,11,FCardiff Crown Court heard his offences
OL,12,Fwere "not similar in character or
OL,13,Fnature," and that activating the
OL,14,Fsuspended sentence would be "unjust"
OL,15,Fin this case.
